(
<figureCitation id="66A82A7DFFD9FF87FF0AFEFDFF117C13" box="[190,250,288,310]" captionStart="Map 5" captionStartId="43.[108,152,1039,1060]" captionTargetBox="[106,1096,174,1022]" captionTargetId="figure-86@43.[106,1096,174,1022]" captionTargetPageId="43" captionText="Map 5: Distributions of species in the Heteromeringia czernyi species group excluding H. czernyi KERTESZ. Legend: H. flavipes ((WILLIST WILLISTON), circle; H. flavifrons HENNIG, dot." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752062" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4752062/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="54">Map 5</figureCitation>
